channel.title: Ekstrak & Trey - First Flight (Ekstrak’s VIP) [DnB, Electro]
channel.description:
![image|499x499](upload://wGtPYq62oyZ6ORGLWvugVUHpWDD.jpeg) https://soundcloud.com/xtrk/first-flight-vip
Hey? Remember that one trak I did with @Trey a year back? Well, I decided to make a Drum and Bass VIP Version of it. Also, my first trak made with Auxy 6, so with that in mind, this trak is an experiment to see what I can do with this Auxy 6.
So, thanks for listening, and feel free to leave any feedback or constructive criticism!
